---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="KickzBrary"
  description="Organize, track, and explore your personal sneaker collection with KickzBrary."
>
  <section class="page-hero container">
    <p class="eyebrow">KickzBrary</p>
    <div class="page-app-icon">
      <img
        src="/icons/kickzbrary.png"
        alt="KickzBrary app icon"
        class="app-icon"
      />
    </div>
    <h1>Your sneaker collection, organized.</h1>
    <p>
      KickzBrary helps sneaker enthusiasts catalog, organize, and explore their
      personal collections in one thoughtfully designed app.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="content-card">
    <h2>About KickzBrary</h2>
    <p>
      KickzBrary is being built for collectors who want a simple way to keep
      track of the sneakers they own and enjoy their collection as a personal
      sneaker library.
    </p>

    <h2>Features</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Catalog your sneaker collection</li>
      <li>Organize and track your sneakers</li>
      <li>Explore your personal sneaker library</li>
      <li>Privacy-focused design</li>
      <li>A native experience for Apple platforms</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Learn More</h2>
    <p>
      <a href="/support/kickzbrary">Support</a>
      · <a href="/privacy/kickzbrary">Privacy Policy</a>
      · <a href="/accessibility/kickzbrary">Accessibility</a>
    </p>

    <h2>Status</h2>
    <p>KickzBrary is currently in active development and coming soon.</p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
